  ('investigation-d5dfc642-moex-00010', 'investigation-d5dfc642', 'investigation-d5dfc642-moex-114-d7e58de3', 'sub-investigation-d5dfc642-03', NULL, 'essay', '甲以其所有之貨輪載運乙的貨物至澳洲墨爾本途中，由於船長未遵守海
